Vendored tools — bundled into the macOS app alongside scripts/.

exiftool   Perl script + lib/ from Image-ExifTool distribution (exiftool.org).
           Currently v13.50. To update: download a new tar.gz, replace
           exiftool and lib/.

tag        macOS Finder tag CLI (github.com/jdberry/tag).
           Copy from Homebrew: cp $(brew --prefix)/bin/tag scripts/tools/tag
